      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4047 - Abu Abdullah Muhammad ibn Khalid al-Barqi (may Allah (swt) be pleased with him) narrated from Wahb ibn Wahb, from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said:\n\"None consume from lost property except those who are themselves lost.\""
        ]
